																	<h3 class="mark_name colorDeep" tabindex="0">7. <span class="colorShallow">(单选题, 1分)</span><span class="qtContent workTextWrap"><p>用条件运算符定义一个过程<br>正确的定义是:</p></span></h3>
								
																	<ul class="mark_letter colorDeep qtDetail">
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">A. <p>(define (f x y) (cond ((x&gt;y) (* x x x))<br>((x=y) 0)<br>((x&lt;y) (* y y y))))</p></li>
																																																																																	<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">B. <p>(define (f x y) (cond ((&gt; x y) (* x x x))<br>((= x y) 0)<br>((&lt; x y) (* y y y))))</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">C. <p>(define (f x y) (cond (( x&gt; y) ( x* x* x))<br>(( x= y) 0)<br>(( x&lt; y) ( y* y* y))))</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">D. <p>(define (f x y) (cond ((&lt; x y) (* x x x))<br>((= x y) 0)<br>((&gt; x y) (* y y y))))</p></li>
																		</ul>
									
									<div class="mark_answer" tabindex="0">
