							<div class="marBom60 questionLi singleQuesId" style="word-wrap: break-word;" id="question404312859" data="404312859" tabindex="0" aria-label="题目详情">
								<div class="aiArea">
								<div class="aiAreaContent">
																	<h3 class="mark_name colorDeep" tabindex="0">8. <span class="colorShallow">(单选题, 1分)</span><span class="qtContent workTextWrap"><p>关于“递归”，下列说法不正确的是:</p></span></h3>
								
																	<ul class="mark_letter colorDeep qtDetail">
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">A. <p>“递归”源自于数学上的递推式和数学归纳法</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">B. <p>“递归”是自后项(即第n项)向前项(第n-1项)代入，直到递归基础获取结果，再从前项计算后项获取结果，直到获得最终结果</p></li>
																																																																																	<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">C. <p>“递归”与递推式一样，都是自递推基础计算起，由前项(第n-1项)计算后项(第n项)，直到获得最终结果</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">D. <p>“递归”是由前n-1项计算第n项的一种方法</p></li>
																		</ul>
									
									<div class="mark_answer" tabindex="0">
										<div class="mark_key clearfix">
											<span class="colorDeep marginRight40 fl"><i class="fontWeight custom-style">我的答案:</i><span class="stuAnswerContent">C</span></span>
											<span class="element-invisible-hidden colorDeep marginRight40 fl">:“递归”与递推式一样，都是自递推基础计算起，由前项(第n-1项)计算后项(第n项)，直到获得最终结果; </span>
																							<span class="colorGreen marginRight40 fl"><i class="fontWeight custom-style">正确答案:</i><span class="rightAnswerContent workTextWrap">C</span></span>
											<span class="element-invisible-hidden colorGreen marginRight40 fl">:“递归”与递推式一样，都是自递推基础计算起，由前项(第n-1项)计算后项(第n项)，直到获得最终结果; </span>
																					</div>
										<div class="mark_score">
											<div class=" fl catalog_tishi80">
																								<div class="mark_judge_name">
																										<span class="marking_dui"></span>
