							<div class="marBom60 questionLi singleQuesId" style="word-wrap: break-word;" id="question404312861" data="404312861" tabindex="0" aria-label="题目详情">
								<div class="aiArea">
								<div class="aiAreaContent">
																	<h3 class="mark_name colorDeep" tabindex="0">10. <span class="colorShallow">(单选题, 1分)</span><span class="qtContent workTextWrap"><p>Fibnoacci数列与Ackermann函数都是递归函数(如下所示)，但它们是不同的，下列说法不正确的是:<br><img src="https://p.ananas.chaoxing.com/star3/origin/08123f24d72401f822f0b5722097002d.png"></p></span></h3>
								
																	<ul class="mark_letter colorDeep qtDetail">
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">A. <p>Fibnoacci是原始递归的而 Ackermann函数不是</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">B. <p>Fibnoacci可以递推地计算即迭代计算;Ackermann函数只能递归地计算</p></li>
																																																																																	<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">C. <p>Ackermann函数也可如Fibnoacci数列一样自前项(n-1)计算到后项(n)</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">D. <p>Ackermann函数是双递归函数，不仅函数自身是递归定义的，同时函数的变量也是递归定义的</p></li>
																		</ul>
									
									<div class="mark_answer" tabindex="0">
										<div class="mark_key clearfix">
											<span class="colorDeep marginRight40 fl"><i class="fontWeight custom-style">我的答案:</i><span class="stuAnswerContent">C</span></span>
											<span class="element-invisible-hidden colorDeep marginRight40 fl">:Ackermann函数也可如Fibnoacci数列一样自前项(n-1)计算到后项(n); </span>
																							<span class="colorGreen marginRight40 fl"><i class="fontWeight custom-style">正确答案:</i><span class="rightAnswerContent workTextWrap">C</span></span>
											<span class="element-invisible-hidden colorGreen marginRight40 fl">:Ackermann函数也可如Fibnoacci数列一样自前项(n-1)计算到后项(n); </span>
																					</div>
