																																																																																	<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">B. <p>(define (secondCalc x y z) (+(firstCalc x) (firstCalc y) (firstCalc z)))</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">C. <p>(define secondCalc (+ (firstCalc x) (firstCalc x) (firstCalc x)))</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">D. <p>(define secondCalc x y z (+ (firstCalc x) (firstCalc x) (firstCalc x)))</p></li>
