																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">B. <p>a ( ( b c -) d * ) +</p></li>
																																																																																	<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">C. <p>a + (b - c) * d</p></li>
																																							<li tabindex="0" class="workTextWrap">D. <p>a b ( c - + d )</p></li>
																		</ul>
									
