							<div class="marBom60 questionLi singleQuesId" style="word-wrap: break-word;" id="question404312886" data="404312886" tabindex="0" aria-label="题目详情">
								<div class="aiArea">
								<div class="aiAreaContent">
																	<h3 class="mark_name colorDeep" tabindex="0">35. <span class="colorShallow">(简答题, 10分)</span><span class="qtContent workTextWrap"><p>请你构造一个过程f(x)=x<sup>3</sup>再以过程f(x)为基础构造一个新过程g(x,y,z)=x<sup>3</sup>+y<sup>3</sup>+z<sup>3</sup>,再以过程g(x,y,z)为基础构造一个新过程m(x,y,z)，m(x,y,z)=(x+1)<sup>3</sup>+(2y)<sup>3</sup>+(z+x)<sup>3</sup><br>请用(define语言来写)</p></span></h3>
								
																	<div class="mark_answer" tabindex="0">
										<div class="mark_answer_key pad0">
											<dl class="mark_fill colorDeep" id="qb404312886">
												<dt class="positionStyle"><i class="fontWeight custom-style">我的答案：</i>
													<div class="mark_score">
																												<div class="totalScore fr">
															<i class="custom-style">10</i>分														</div>
																											</div>
												</dt>

																																				
												<dd class="textwrap stuAnswerContent reserve-newline"><p>define (f x) (* x x x)</p><p>define (g x y z) ( + f(x) f(y) f(z) )</p><p>define (m x y z) ( +f(+x 1) f(*2 y) f(+z x) )<br/></p></dd>
											</dl>
																						<dl class="mark_fill colorGreen">
												<dt><i class="fontWeight custom-style"> 正确答案：</i></dt>
																								<dd class="rightAnswerContent workTextWrap"><p>define (f x) (* x x x)<br>define (g x y z) (+ f(x) f(y) f(z))<br>define (m x y z) (g((+ 1 x), (* 2 y),(+ z x)))</p></dd>
																							</dl>
																					</div>
																				<!--显示知识点-->
        <div class="knowledgePointBx colorGray">
        <span class="answerFont fl" style="line-height: 30px;">知识点：</span>
        <div class="fl answerCon">
            <ul class="knowledgeList">
                                    <li  topicid="96307774"  title="">
