							<div class="marBom60 questionLi singleQuesId" style="word-wrap: break-word;" id="question404312887" data="404312887" tabindex="0" aria-label="题目详情">
								<div class="aiArea">
								<div class="aiAreaContent">
																	<h3 class="mark_name colorDeep" tabindex="0">36. <span class="colorShallow">(简答题, 10分)</span><span class="qtContent workTextWrap"><p>程序是构造出来的，程序构造能力需要不断地训练，请你以课本中的表达方法:括号、前缀表示法、define以及条件表达cond将下列计算式表达为程序:(不要化简表达式)<br><img src="https://p.ananas.chaoxing.com/star3/origin/9e04a4d72ab77bf9f1de090a4eb8b690.png"></p></span></h3>
								
																	<div class="mark_answer" tabindex="0">
										<div class="mark_answer_key pad0">
											<dl class="mark_fill colorDeep" id="qb404312887">
												<dt class="positionStyle"><i class="fontWeight custom-style">我的答案：</i>
													<div class="mark_score">
																												<div class="totalScore fr">
															<i class="custom-style">10</i>分														</div>
																											</div>
												</dt>

																																				
												<dd class="textwrap stuAnswerContent reserve-newline"><p>define (f n)(*2 n)</p><p>define (g n) ( +(-( f n ) 1 ) ) &nbsp;( +(f n) 1 ) )&nbsp; <br/></p><p>define (sum n mc)(sum_i 0 1 n)</p><p>define (sum_i s c mc)(cond( (&gt; c mc) s )((&lt;= c mc)</p><p>(sum_i(/1 (sumpdd n))(+ c 1) mc ))<br/></p><p><br/></p></dd>
											</dl>
																						<dl class="mark_fill colorGreen">
												<dt><i class="fontWeight custom-style"> 正确答案：</i></dt>
																								<dd class="rightAnswerContent workTextWrap"><p>define (dup n) (* 2 n)<br>define (sumodd n) (+ (- (dup n) 1) (+ (dup n) 1))<br>define (sum n mc) (sum_iter 0 1 n)<br>define (sum_iter s c mc ) (cond ((&gt; c mc) s)<br>((&lt;= c mc)<br>(sum_iter (/ 1 (sumodd n)) (+ c 1) mc))<br>)</p></dd>
																							</dl>
																					</div>
																				<!--显示知识点-->
        <div class="knowledgePointBx colorGray">
        <span class="answerFont fl" style="line-height: 30px;">知识点：</span>
        <div class="fl answerCon">
            <ul class="knowledgeList">
                                    <li  topicid="96316377"  title="">
                        <a  target="_blank" href="https://mooc2-ans.chaoxing.com/mooc2-ans/mycourse/stu?courseid=244670737&clazzid=102842771&cpi=408105850&microTopicId=96316377&&enc=607137cf349578a37586f6495101b780&t=1781812287164" >递归/迭代执行</a>
                    </li>
                            </ul>
        </div>
